      "content": "## 1) STRUCTURE ANALYSIS (what\u2019s in the molecule)\n**SMILES:** `CCn1cc(C(=O)[O-])c(=O)c2cc(F)c(N3CC[NH2+][C@H](C)C3)c(F)c21`",
