      "step_type": "reasoning",
      "content": "## 4) PREDICTION + CONFIDENCE\n**PREDICTION:** **Negative** (unlikely to be a strong hERG blocker; if any activity, more likely weak/moderate rather than high-risk blockade)  \n**CONFIDENCE:** **Medium** (because 3D conformation, actual pKa microstates, and transporter-mediated access can change effective exposure to the channel)",
